where formula_89 is the formula_3-th observation on the formula_91-th independent variable.
If the first independent variable takes the value 1 for all formula_3, formula_93, then formula_57 is called the regression intercept.

The least squares parameter estimates are obtained from formula_81 normal equations. The residual can be written as

:formula_96

The normal equations are

:formula_97

