<doc id="827124" wikidata="Q5762249" url="?curid=827124" title="Hill Rag">
<text>The Hill Rag is a community newspaper based in Washington, D.C.&#x27;s Capitol Hill neighborhood. It is published monthly. In addition to Capitol Hill, it provides coverage of the Southwest Waterfront, H Street Northeast, and Navy Yard neighborhoods. The &quot;Hill Rag&quot; is owned by Capital Community News Inc., one of the largest publishing firms of community-based publications in the United States, which also owns several other DC newspapers and publications.

It should not be confused with &quot;The Hill&quot;, a weekly newspaper covering the United States Congress.

