*&quot;Alien Secrets&quot; (1993, Delacorte)
*&quot;Blood and Chocolate&quot; (1997, Delacorte)
*&quot;&quot; (2006, Margaret K. McElderry)

===Other publications===
Klause contributed book reviews to the &quot;School Library Journal&quot; from 1982 through 1994.

