:C05AD04 Cinchocaine
:C05AD05 Procaine
:C05AD06 Oxetacaine
:C05AD07 Pramocaine

===C05AE Muscle relaxants===
:C05AE01 Glyceryl trinitrate
:C05AE02 Isosorbide dinitrate
:C05AE03 Diltiazem

===C05AX Other agents for treatment of hemorrhoids and anal fissures for topical use===
